Each phase is executed by plugins.
Each plugin offers multiple goals.
Goal is a task which is executed by a plugin.
Mvn cmd
Phase
plugin:goal
compile
compiler:compile
test-compile
compiler:testCompile
test
surefire:test
package
jar:jar
 
Maven commands follow the below syntax:
mvn [phase]
mvn [plugin name]:[goal]
These are the phases we are going to execute in our project:
                                      	
                          	          POM.xml(dev)




























 
 
 

           	Reads pom
Maven  
 
 
 
 
1)read the pom.xml
2)downloads the plugins into local repo and executes the tasks
 
 
Tasks
plugins
mvn command
compile
 Compiler 
mvn compile
Code Review
Pmd plugin
mvn pmd:pmd
Unit Test
Surefire Plugin
mvn test
Coverage Analysis
Cobertura plugin
mvn cobertura:cobertura
Package
Jar plugin
mvn package
 
Compile:
Maven compiler plugin:
mvn compile
